sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist<br/>Browser/SDK
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant API as DS Pipeline API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP TLS1.3
    participant WFC as Workflow Controller<br/>Argo Workflows
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Pod as Pipeline Pod
    participant S3 as Minio/S3<br/>9000/TCP or 443/TCP
    participant DB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP MySQL TLS1.2+
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>gRPC TLS1.3
    participant PA as Persistence Agent

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 1: Pipeline Submission

    User->>Route: POST /apis/v2beta1/pipelines<br/>OAuth2 Token
    Route->>OAuth: Forward request<br/>TLS termination
    OAuth->>OAuth: Validate OAuth2 token
    OAuth->>API: Forward to API server<br/>TLS 1.3 pod-to-pod
    API->>DB: Store pipeline definition<br/>MySQL protocol
    DB-->>API: Success
    API->>WFC: Create Workflow CR<br/>gRPC/HTTP TLS1.3
    API-->>User: Pipeline created<br/>JSON response

    Note over WFC,S3: Flow 2: Pipeline Execution

    WFC->>K8s: Create Pipeline Pod<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8s-->>WFC: Pod created
    WFC->>Pod: Start execution
    Pod->>S3: Download input artifacts<br/>S3 Access Keys
    S3-->>Pod: Artifacts
    Pod->>Pod: Execute ML code
    Pod->>S3: Upload output artifacts<br/>S3 Access Keys
    Pod->>API: Report execution status<br/>8887/TCP gRPC TLS1.3
    API->>MLMD: Record metadata<br/>9090/TCP gRPC/HTTP2 TLS1.3
    MLMD->>DB: Store ML metadata
    Pod-->>WFC: Completion status

    Note over PA,DB: Flow 3: State Persistence

    PA->>K8s: Watch Workflow CRs<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8s-->>PA: Workflow state changes
    PA->>API: Sync workflow state<br/>8887/TCP gRPC TLS1.3
    API->>DB: Update run status<br/>3306/TCP MySQL
    DB-->>API: Stored
    API-->>PA: Acknowledged

    Note over User,DB: Flow 4: Query Results

    User->>Route: GET /apis/v2beta1/runs/{id}<br/>OAuth2 Token
    Route->>OAuth: Forward<br/>TLS1.2+
    OAuth->>API: Authenticated request<br/>TLS1.3
    API->>DB: Query run details<br/>MySQL
    DB-->>API: Run data
    API->>S3: Get artifact URLs<br/>Signed URLs
    S3-->>API: Presigned URLs
    API-->>User: Run details + artifact links<br/>JSON
